title: Justin Bieber: 'I Have Such Great Music That I Want to Share With the World'
text: Justin Bieber shows off some sick tricks while skateboarding at Sydney Olympic Park Wharf before hopping on a water taxi on Wednesday (September 30) in Sydney, Australia. The 21-year-old singer recently opened up about his upcoming new album. “I’ll hear songs on the radio, and I’m not really a fan of what’s going on right [...] »
